  "title": "Culinary Leader / Head Chef (Modern Chinese Kitchen)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Title: Culinary Leader / Head Chef – Modern Chinese Kitchen</strong></p><h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Lead & Inspire the Team:</strong> Guide, mentor, and develop our kitchen staff. Foster a culture of growth, mutual respect, and shared purpose.</p></li><li><p><strong>Master the Wok:</strong> Take command of our core station. Consistently execute our signature Mala and modern Chinese dishes that define our menu.</p></li><li><p><strong>Guardian of Standards:</strong> Be the ultimate owner of quality, hygiene, and consistency in every ingredient, plate, and process.</p></li><li><p><strong>Drive Seamless Service:</strong> Partner closely with our front-of-house team to ensure a smooth, synchronized flow from kitchen to guest.</p></li><li><p><strong>Develop Talent:</strong> Identify and nurture the skills of your team members, helping them grow in their careers.</p></li><li><p><strong>Own the Kitchen:</strong> Take full responsibility for maintaining a safe, efficient, organized, and inspiring workspace.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Have <strong>3+ years of hands-on experience leading a team</strong> in a fast-paced commercial kitchen.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
